{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3450880/extras/Gif-Archer11.gif?t=1739123283\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on a relentless journey through a dark, perilous world in this intense action RPG. Fight to survive overwhelming hordes, conquer towering bosses, and unravel the secrets hidden within a world shrouded in mystery. Upgrade your abilities, find powerful equipment, and shape your hero to overcome the enemies.<br><br><strong>Permanent leveling up</strong>, as well as <strong>progression within each run</strong>.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Distribute your <strong>experience points</strong> across different stats.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Abilities include both <strong>manual aiming</strong> and <strong>some automatic skills</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Randomized skill system</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Slower, Souls-like combat</strong>, but facing both <strong>large enemy hordes</strong> and <strong>smaller, stronger, and more complex enemy groups</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Large maps</strong> with enemies in different rooms\u2014some can be skipped, others require completing objectives, and there are also <strong>optional rooms</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Limited items</strong> you can bring into each run (<strong>health potions, rerolls, etc.</strong>).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Timers</strong>, allowing for <strong>map speedruns</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Boss fights!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3450880/extras/Gif-Archer9.gif?t=1739123283\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3450880/